Title: The zero-curvature representation for nonlinear O(3) sigma-model

Authors: A.G.Bytsko

Comments: Uppsala University preprint, 12 pages, LaTeX file

Journal-ref: Zap.Nauchn.Semin. 215 (1994) 100-114

We consider O(3) sigma-model as a reduction of the principal chiral field.This approach allows to introduce the currents with ultralocalPoisson brackets and to obtain the zero-curvature equation which admits thefundamental Poisson bracket.